  		<li class="slide1">
  			<h6>Spotlight</h6>
  			<h2><a href="http://www.criterion.com/films/784-an-autumn-afternoon">Last Ozu</a></h2>
  			<p>Yasujiro Ozu’s poignant, beautifully shot final film, <i>An Autumn Afternoon,</i> about a widower coming to terms with his daughter’s marriage, is available this week for the first time on Blu-ray.</p>
  			<a href="http://www.criterion.com/films/784-an-autumn-afternoon" class="readmore" title="Read more">Learn more</a>
  			<a href="http://www.criterion.com/films/784-an-autumn-afternoon" class="spotlight_link">&nbsp;</a>
  		</li>
